ji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實你都明知佢而家咁樣遲早會搞第二個<br />\n何必又自欺欺人咁呃自己佢唔會出軌呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早啲分手 認清事實佢唔愛你啦<br />\n會無咁傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都好驚會有一日發現呢d事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日都日驚夜驚 擔心到個人勁灰 好似殘左咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一同佢分手 佢次次都自殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2f9566f02ae621645db81d1e32276471149dea","tid":396330,"uid":19072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T17:44:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b2cc3928a6fb0423f43eb3d9d6ba3bc7ca5d191","tid":396330,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T17:48:57.000Z","msg":"早啲散啦<br />\n你愛佢多過佢愛你<br />\n而佢係愛你，不過唔係好愛囉"}]}